| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3872 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 93f24f89-1cb1-5507-92f9-2e84362ea9de"
